Build Dependancy:
	Qt toolkit >= 4.5:
		http://trolltech.com/products
	Loki -- Generic Programming and Design Pattern library for C++:
		http://loki-lib.sourceforge.net

Build toolchain:
	Unix-like:
		g++ >= 4
	Windows (XP or Vista):
		Visual C++ >= Express 2005

How to Build:
	Unix-like:
		$ qmake
		$ make -j2
	Windows:
		> qmake -tp vc
		Open komix.vcproj with Visual C++ and build

Run-time spec @ Windows:
	dll provide by MSVC:
		You may just install Redistributable Package for your machine.
		http://www.microsoft.com/downloads/details.aspx?familyid=A5C84275-3B97-4AB7-A40D-3802B2AF5FC2&displaylang=en
	dll provide by Qt toolkit
